  "page": "Roland of the Horn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Roland of the Horn</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nRoland of the Horn</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (Mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Roland of the Horn</b> is a legendary <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> who lived during the <a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a>. Tales describe him as a knight even though knights came to <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> thousands of years later with the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roland_of_the_Horn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\